query: SELECT cc.componentName, i.vesselTagNumber, cc.reportId, cc.actualThickness FROM componentCalculations cc JOIN professionalReports pr ON cc.reportId = pr.id JOIN inspections i ON pr.inspectionId = i.id ORDER BY i.vesselTagNumber, cc.componentName;
